title: TUESDAY - MNF game of the year? 2020
itunes:title: TUESDAY - MNF game of the year? 2020
description:
Monday Night Football brought us a nail biter between the Ravens and Browns (0:09). Baltimore pulling out the win behind a heroic performance by Lamar Jackson as he dealt with cramps (1:45). The QB situation (3:05) in Philadelphia has some clarity...for now. Plus, the latest on Mike McCarthy's future in Dallas
